(284, 84, 'description', 'This is an internal initiative (and 1 of 3 initiatives for LexisNexis). \r\nThe timeline can be found here: http://publish.smartsheet.com/b2595dd6bece45639bad6fa52bb430eb\r\n\r\nPrize Structure\r\nPrize draw:  1 Apple iPad (version 3) and a second draw for 1 Google Nexus 7 or Kindle Fire (preferred, depending on availability) tablet - random drawing from all participants using the following draw entry earning process:\r\n\r\n    1 entry for signing up and completing the minimum level of participation in the first round of activities\r\n    1 additional entry for achieving a minimum level of participation in each of the remaining two rounds of activities\r\n    1 additional entry for reaching 1,500 points and 1 more additional entry for reaching 3,000 points.\r\n    Each participant can earn up to 5 entries in total.\r\n\r\nTop 2 participants based on points:  Two Google Nexus 7 or Kindle Fire (preferred, depending on availability) tablets\r\nHow do participants earn points?\r\n    Exceptional participation awards (awarded to 2 people per round)  - 250 points\r\n    Minimum discussion topic participation - 50 points\r\n    Top 3 voted submission on select discussion topics - 100 points\r\n    Completion of optional profile fields  - 100 points\r\n    100 votes cast on others'' submissions - 25 points\r\n    Receive 10 "up" or "me too" votes in on your submissions/answers from other participants  - 5 points\r\n    Receive 10 "likes" on your comments from other participants  - 5 points'),
