(312, 84, 'additional_program_instructions', 'Update the following badges (should be made on base):\r\n\r\nEnthusiast - Awarded to participants who are repeat visitors to the community.\r\n\r\nInnovator - Awarded to participants who have submitted ideas and received 5 up votes on a submission.\r\n\r\nThought Leader - Awarded to participants who have submitted ideas and received 10 up votes on the submission.\r\n\r\nInitiator - Awarded to participants who are the first members to join a community. <em></em><em>(note: no text changes, but should be assigned to the first 100)</em>\r\n\r\nConversationalist - Awarded to participants who foster conversation and consistently add value to participation through comments.\r\n\r\nOvertimer - Awarded to participants who are involved in multiple activities.\r\n\r\nAutobiographer - Awarded to participants who have provided their full profile details.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nPlease ensure all referencing to "subscriptions" is removed being that you cannot follow in task based communities\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>\r\n</strong></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
