(1222, 150, 'additional_program_instructions', 'When a user clicks on ''Create Account'' on the homepage, they are taken to a screener form.  We will be asking them the following:\r\n\r\n<strong>Basic Contact Information</strong>\r\n\r\nFirst Name\r\n\r\nLast Name\r\n\r\nDisplay Name\r\n\r\nEmail\r\n\r\nAddress\r\n\r\nCity\r\n\r\nProvince\r\n\r\nPostal Code\r\n\r\n<strong>Basic info about you</strong>\r\n\r\nGender  (Male/Female)\r\n\r\nWhat is the highest level of education that you have completed?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Some High School</li>\r\n	<li>High School Graduate or Equivalent</li>\r\n	<li>Trade or Vocational Degree</li>\r\n	<li>Some College</li>\r\n	<li>Associate Degree</li>\r\n	<li>Bachelor''s Degree</li>\r\n	<li>Graduate of Professional Degree</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhat is your current employment status?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li> Employed Full-Time</li>\r\n	<li>Employed Part-Time</li>\r\n	<li>Self-employed</li>\r\n	<li>Not employed, but looking for work</li>\r\n	<li>Not employed and not looking for work</li>\r\n	<li>Homemaker</li>\r\n	<li>Retired</li>\r\n	<li>Student</li>\r\n	<li>Prefer Not to Answer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhat is your total household income?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li> under $20,000</li>\r\n	<li>$20,000 - $30,000</li>\r\n	<li>$30,000 - $40,000</li>\r\n	<li>$40,000 - $50,000</li>\r\n	<li>$50,000 - $75,000</li>\r\n	<li>$75,000 - $100,000</li>\r\n	<li>$100,000 - $150,000</li>\r\n	<li>$150,000 or more</li>\r\n	<li>Do not know</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you were to win a gift card, which would you choose?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>McDonald’s</li>\r\n	<li>Subway</li>\r\n	<li>Starbucks</li>\r\n	<li>Tim Horton’s</li>\r\n	<li>Safeway</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAnd why?\r\n\r\n[ ]  I am 19 years or older and am legally allowed to enter into a contract without parental consent.'),
