(124, 3, '2012-08-20 13:17:30', '2012-08-20 20:17:30', '	<h2>Phased Collaboration Dashboard:</h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>We are going to need additional systems for indicating information for Phased collaboration dashboards. Most of this information can be included in a word document <strong>provided that</strong> the Word document contains all of the relevant information. This information should include (per phase)</p>\r\n\r\n	<h3>Overall information for Phased system:</h3>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Pages to display the phased timeline (How it works, login, rewards, homepage, idea list, idea submission)</li>\r\n		<li>Additional Skinning for the phased timeline?</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>DEFAULT: Admins are always able to edit ideas\r\n\r\n	<h3>Phase Specific information for the Phased system:</h3>\r\n\r\n		<li>Does any content anywhere on the site other than the phased timeline/idea list/idea view change as a result of this flip?</li>\r\n		<li>If yes, where, and to what?</li>\r\n		<li>Phase number</li>\r\n		<li>Phase name (if applicable)</li>\r\n		<li>Phase dates (associated with phase number)</li>\r\n		<li>Submissions open? (y/n)</li>\r\n		<li>Idea editing allowed? (y/n)</li>\r\n		<li>Additional fields open for editing? (y/n)</li>\r\n		<li>Voting (y/n)</li>\r\n		<li>Voting instructions</li>\r\n		<li>Voting style</li>\r\n		<li>Manual idea selection (y/n)</li>\r\n		<li>Flags set by manual idea selection? (y/n)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Which flags? (Finalist, crowd favorite, etc.)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n ', 'Bibles: Mandatory Phase flip information', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bibles-mandatory-phase-flip-information', '', '', '2012-08-20 13:17:30', '2012-08-20 20:17:30', '', 0, 'https://delivery.chaordix.com/?page_id=124', 0, 'page', '', 0),
