(131, 3, '2012-08-20 15:00:36', '2012-08-20 22:00:36', '<h2>Program Type:</h2>\nThe Program Type should contain a significant amount more information. Specifically, both kinds of dashboards require additional information based on their types.\n<h2>Task Dashboard options:</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>“There are no current activities” Text</li>\n	<li>“You didn’t complete last week’s activities!” Text</li>\n	<li>“Congrats! You’ve completed everything this week!” Text</li>\n	<li>“Participate in activities to receive (checkmark image) and earn <a href="http://points">points</a></li>\n	<li>Drafts window (additional options?)</li>\n	<li>Quick Questions</li>\n	<li>Round title text (Round 4, etc.)</li>\n	<li>Special completion text for completing activities (“You’ve earned 50 points!”)</li>\n	<li>Partners widget (“Learn more about (blank)”)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Collaboration Dashboard options:</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>Title (“My Dashboard”)</li>\n	<li>Drafts window (additional options?)</li>\n	<li>Activity Sorting bar (additional options?)</li>\n	<li>Activity Feed (additional options?</li>\n	<li>Quick Questions</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Widgets:</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>Automagically updating Blog widget</li>\n	<li>Access to previous weeks widget</li>\n	<li>Avatar Window (additional options?)</li>\n	<li>Settings widget</li>\n	<li>Rewards widget</li>\n	<li>Welcome video</li>\n	<li>Avatar window</li>\n	<li>Following window</li>\n	<li>Badges Window</li>\n	<li>New/top submissions window</li>\n	<li>Automagically updating Blog widget</li>\n	<li>Partners widget (“Learn more about <em>blank</em>”)</li>\n</ul>', 'Bibles: Program Type', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '103-autosave', '', '', '2012-08-20 15:00:36', '2012-08-20 22:00:36', '', 103, 'https://delivery.chaordix.com/103-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
